snippet.title: Dogs are garbage  aka Ashley
snippet.description:
I am a former animal trainer and now a dog hater.  I intend to spread awareness with an open heart and mind, dog haters are welcome here with open arms and dog lovers are also welcome to inform themselves on the facts and statistics of dog attacks. This channel is about dog hatred and presenting the facts so buckle your seat belts people and keep your weapons close!  
From the bottom of my dog hating heart I appreciate every single one of you. ❤️
Email me at :
ashleylynn420@icloud.com
With stories, recent articles or just to say hello. ❤️
You can also find me on fb.  Ashley Blackburn 
If you want to donate please do so on pay pal: 
ashleylynn420@icloud.com 
Is the email that is associated with my card. 
If you do just know that it helps me to continue making daily content. Thank you :)!  !

I am not a lawyer. I am not giving legal advice. These are stories and statistics.  I am not responsible for your actions.
